---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="The Knowledge Economy" description="Your expertise becomes equity. Value flows, pricing models, and what Synthesis enables.">
  <!-- Hero -->
  <section class="section pt-12 sm:pt-16">
    <div class="container-wide">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-start">
        <div class="fade-section">
          <p class="text-sm font-medium text-accent-600 dark:text-accent-400 mb-2 uppercase tracking-wide">Economics</p>
          <h1 class="heading-1 mb-4">Your expertise becomes <span class="gradient-text">equity</span>.</h1>
          <p class="body-large text-synthesis-600 dark:text-synthesis-400 mb-6">
            The fundamental shift: expertise becomes an asset you own, not just a capacity you rent out.
          </p>
          <div class="flex gap-6 sm:gap-8 text-base">
            <div>
              <p class="text-synthesis-500 mb-1">Traditional</p>
              <p class="text-synthesis-800 dark:text-synthesis-200">Sell time → knowledge leaves</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-accent-600 dark:text-accent-400 mb-1">Synthesis</p>
              <p class="text-synthesis-800 dark:text-synthesis-200">Sell cognition → value flows back</p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Three Value Flows -->
  <section class="section-narrow border-t border-synthesis-100 dark:border-synthesis-900">
    <div class="container-wide">
      <div class="fade-section mb-6 sm:mb-8">
        <h2 class="heading-2 mb-2">Three Value Flows</h2>
      </div>
      
      <div class="fade-section grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 sm:gap-8 lg:gap-12">
        <!-- Direct Sale -->
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-synthesis-800 dark:text-synthesis-200 mb-2">1. Direct Sale</h3>
          <p class="text-base text-synthesis-600 dark:text-synthesis-400 mb-4">
            Create a pack, sell it outright. Multiple organizations can buy the same expertise.
          </p>
          <div class="font-mono text-sm text-synthesis-600 dark:text-synthesis-400 space-y-1">
            <p>Pack → Org A <span class="text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400">$5k</span></p>
            <p>Pack → Org B <span class="text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400">$5k</span></p>
            <p>Pack → Org C <span class="text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400">$5k</span></p>
            <p class="text-synthesis-800 dark:text-synthesis-200 pt-2 border-t border-synthesis-200 dark:border-synthesis-800 mt-2">You receive: $15,000</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Licensing -->
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-synthesis-800 dark:text-synthesis-200 mb-2">2. Licensing</h3>
          <p class="text-base text-synthesis-600 dark:text-synthesis-400 mb-4">
            Ongoing access with recurring payments. Updates included as expertise evolves.
          </p>
          <div class="font-mono text-sm text-synthesis-600 dark:text-synthesis-400 space-y-1">
            <p>Pack → Org A <span class="text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400">$500/mo</span></p>
            <p>Pack → Org B <span class="text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400">$500/mo</span></p>
            <p class="text-synthesis-800 dark:text-synthesis-200 pt-2 border-t border-synthesis-200 dark:border-synthesis-800 mt-2">You receive: $1,000/mo ongoing</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        
        <!-- Lineage Royalties -->
        <div>
          <h3 class="text-base font-semibold text-accent-600 dark:text-accent-400 mb-2">3. Lineage Royalties ✦</h3>
          <p class="text-base text-synthesis-600 dark:text-synthesis-400 mb-4">
            The transformative model. Value flows backward through the knowledge graph.
          </p>
          <div class="font-mono text-sm text-synthesis-600 dark:text-synthesis-400 space-y-1">
            <p>A creates Pack A</p>
            <p>B builds on A → Pack B</p>
            <p>B sold for <span class="text-synthesis-800 dark:text-synthesis-200">$1,000</span></p>
            <p class="pt-2 border-t border-synthesis-200 dark:border-synthesis-800 mt-2">
              B gets <span class="text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400">$800</span>, 
              A gets <span class="text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400">$200</span>
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <div class="fade-section mt-8 pt-6 border-t border-synthesis-100 dark:border-synthesis-800">
        <p class="text-base text-synthesis-700 dark:text-synthesis-300">
          <strong class="text-synthesis-800 dark:text-synthesis-200">Lineage compounds:</strong> 
          Each layer takes 80%, passes 20% upstream. A→B→C→D sold for $1000: D gets $800, C gets $160, B gets $32, A gets $8. 
          <span class="text-synthesis-500">Foundational work generates value indefinitely.</span>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- For Individuals -->
  <section class="section-narrow border-t border-synthesis-100 dark:border-synthesis-900" id="for-individuals">
    <div class="container-wide">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 sm:gap-8">
        <div class="fade-section">
          <h2 class="heading-3 mb-2">For Individuals</h2>
          <p class="text-base text-synthesis-600 dark:text-synthesis-400">
            Build a knowledge portfolio. AI collaboration compresses the timeline dramatically.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="lg:col-span-2 fade-section">
          <!-- Career comparison - simple two column -->
          <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 sm:gap-8 mb-6 sm:mb-8">
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm text-synthesis-500 mb-3 uppercase tracking-wide">Traditional Career</p>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-base text-synthesis-600 dark:text-synthesis-400">
                <li><span class="text-synthesis-500">Years 1-5:</span> Learn on the job</li>
                <li><span class="text-synthesis-500">Years 5-15:</span> Apply skills, get promoted</li>
                <li><span class="text-synthesis-500">Years 15-30:</span> Senior roles, high salary</li>
                <li><span class="text-synthesis-500">Years 30+:</span> Retire, knowledge disperses</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm text-accent-600 dark:text-accent-400 mb-3 uppercase tracking-wide">Synthesis Career</p>
              <ul class="space-y-2 text-base text-synthesis-700 dark:text-synthesis-300">
                <li><span class="text-synthesis-500">Months 1-3:</span> Learn <strong>and</strong> create first packs</li>
                <li><span class="text-synthesis-500">Months 3-12:</span> Portfolio compounds, derivatives emerge</li>
                <li><span class="text-synthesis-500">Year 1+:</span> Passive income rivals salary</li>
                <li><span class="text-synthesis-500">Perpetual:</span> Packs keep earning via lineage</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Example - adjusted for compressed timeline -->
          <div class="pt-6 border-t border-synthesis-100 dark:border-synthesis-800">
            <p class="text-sm text-synthesis-500 mb-4">
              Example: <strong class="text-synthesis-700 dark:text-synthesis-300">A distributed systems architect</strong>, 18 months on Synthesis
            </p>
            <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-4 gap-6 text-sm">
              <div>
                <p class="text-synthesis-700 dark:text-synthesis-300 font-medium mb-2">Foundational Packs</p>
                <p class="text-synthesis-500">"Distributed Systems Thinking"</p>
                <p class="text-synthesis-400">12 orgs · 4 derivatives</p>
                <p class="text-synthesis-500 mt-2">"CAP Theorem in Practice"</p>
                <p class="text-synthesis-400">8 orgs · 2 derivatives</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-synthesis-700 dark:text-synthesis-300 font-medium mb-2">Specialized Packs</p>
                <p class="text-synthesis-500">"Multi-Region Failover"</p>
                <p class="text-synthesis-400">3 orgs · 1 derivative</p>
                <p class="text-synthesis-500 mt-2">"Event Sourcing Patterns"</p>
                <p class="text-synthesis-400">5 orgs</p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-synthesis-700 dark:text-synthesis-300 font-medium mb-2">High-Value</p>
                <p class="text-synthesis-500">"Zero-Downtime Migration"</p>
                <p class="text-synthesis-400">1 enterprise @ $15k</p>
              </div>
              <div class="sm:border-l sm:border-synthesis-200 sm:dark:border-synthesis-800 sm:pl-6">
                <p class="text-emerald-600 dark:text-emerald-400 font-medium mb-2">Monthly Income</p>
                <p class="text-synthesis-600 dark:text-synthesis-400">Licensing: $2,400</p>
                <p class="text-synthesis-600 dark:text-synthesis-400">Royalties: $600</p>
                <p class="text-synthesis-800 dark:text-synthesis-200 font-semibold mt-2">Total: $3,000/mo</p>
                <p class="text-synthesis-400 text-[10px] mt-1">18 months in, compounding</p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- For Organizations -->
  <section class="section-narrow bg-synthesis-50/50 dark:bg-synthesis-900/20" id="for-organizations">
    <div class="container-wide">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-6 sm:gap-8">
        <div class="fade-section">
          <h2 class="heading-3 mb-2">For Organizations</h2>
          <p class="text-base text-synthesis-600 dark:text-synthesis-400">
            Acquire expertise, not just talent. Knowledge becomes a permanent asset.
          </p>
        </div>
        
        <div class="lg:col-span-2 fade-section">
          <!-- Comparison - minimal -->
          <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 sm:gap-8 mb-6 sm:mb-8">
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm text-synthesis-500 mb-3 uppercase tracking-wide">Traditional: Hire Expertise</p>
              <ul class="space-y-1 text-base text-synthesis-600 dark:text-synthesis-400">
                <li>Find expert <span class="text-synthesis-400">(hard)</span></li>
                <li>Recruit and close <span class="text-synthesis-400">(expensive)</span></li>
                <li>Onboard <span class="text-synthesis-400">(slow)</span></li>
                <li>They might leave <span class="text-synthesis-400">(risky)</span></li>
                <li>Knowledge leaves with them</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm text-accent-600 dark:text-accent-400 mb-3 uppercase tracking-wide">Synthesis: Acquire Expertise</p>
              <ul class="space-y-1 text-base text-synthesis-700 dark:text-synthesis-300">
                <li>Find relevant packs <span class="text-synthesis-400">(searchable)</span></li>
                <li>Verify quality <span class="text-synthesis-400">(cryptographic)</span></li>
                <li>Purchase or license <span class="text-synthesis-400">(instant)</span></li>
                <li>Inject into Commons</li>
                <li><strong>Knowledge stays forever</strong></li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          
          <!-- Startup Example - inline -->
          <div class="pt-6 border-t border-synthesis-200 dark:border-synthesis-800">
            <p class="text-sm text-synthesis-500 mb-4">
              Example: <strong class="text-synthesis-700 dark:text-synthesis-300">AI Startup</strong>, 15 engineers, needs distributed inference expertise
            </p>
            <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6 sm:gap-8 text-base">
              <div>
                <p class="text-synthesis-500 text-sm mb-2">Traditional approach</p>
                <p class="text-synthesis-600 dark:text-synthesis-400">
                  Hire senior distributed systems engineer. 
                  <span class="text-synthesis-500">Timeline: 3-6 months. Cost: $250-400k/year. 
                  Risk: might leave. Knowledge: locked in one head.</span>
                </p>
              </div>
              <div>
                <p class="text-accent-600 dark:text-accent-400 text-sm mb-2">Synthesis approach</p>
                <p class="text-synthesis-700 dark:text-synthesis-300">
                  Acquire two packs for <strong>$25k</strong>. 
                  <span class="text-synthesis-600 dark:text-synthesis-400">Timeline: immediate. 
                  All 15 engineers level up. Knowledge: permanent asset in Commons.</span>
                </p>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- The Flywheel + Trust -->
  <section class="section-narrow border-t border-synthesis-100 dark:border-synthesis-900">
    <div class="container-wide">
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12">
        <div class="fade-section">
          <h2 class="heading-3 mb-4">The Flywheel</h2>
          <p class="text-base text-synthesis-600 dark:text-synthesis-400 mb-4">
            More packs → more adoption → more value to creators → more packs.
          </p>
          <ol class="text-base text-synthesis-600 dark:text-synthesis-400 space-y-2">
            <li><span class="text-synthesis-400 mr-2">1.</span>Experts create packs</li>
            <li><span class="text-synthesis-400 mr-2">2.</span>Organizations acquire packs</li>
            <li><span class="text-synthesis-400 mr-2">3.</span>Organizations become more capable</li>
            <li><span class="text-synthesis-400 mr-2">4.</span><span class="text-accent-600 dark:text-accent-400">Success demonstrates pack value</span></li>
            <li><span class="text-synthesis-400 mr-2">5.</span><span class="text-accent-600 dark:text-accent-400">More demand, more value to experts</span></li>
            <li><span class="text-synthesis-400 mr-2">↻</span>Cycle continues</li>
          </ol>
        </div>
        
        <div class="fade-section">
          <h2 class="heading-3 mb-4">Trust Makes It Work</h2>
          <p class="text-base text-synthesis-600 dark:text-synthesis-400 mb-4">
            Knowledge markets require trust. Synthesis provides it cryptographically—verify, don't trust.
          </p>
          <dl class="text-base space-y-3">
            <div>
              <dt class="text-synthesis-800 dark:text-synthesis-200 font-medium">Verification</dt>
              <dd class="text-synthesis-500">Content hashed and signed. Tampering is impossible.</dd>
            </div>
            <div>
              <dt class="text-synthesis-800 dark:text-synthesis-200 font-medium">Lineage</dt>
              <dd class="text-synthesis-500">See exactly what it built on. Provenance is transparent.</dd>
            </div>
            <div>
              <dt class="text-synthesis-800 dark:text-synthesis-200 font-medium">Reputation</dt>
              <dd class="text-synthesis-500">Track record is public. Gaming requires creating real value.</dd>
            </div>
            <div>
              <dt class="text-synthesis-800 dark:text-synthesis-200 font-medium">Dual attestation</dt>
              <dd class="text-synthesis-500">Human + AI both sign. Independent corroboration.</dd>
            </div>
          </dl>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Core Insight -->
  <section class="section-narrow border-t border-synthesis-100 dark:border-synthesis-900">
    <div class="container-narrow">
      <div class="fade-section text-center">
        <p class="text-base text-synthesis-600 dark:text-synthesis-400 mb-4">
          We've always had knowledge work. We've never had a way to make knowledge 
          <em>work for you</em> after you've created it.
        </p>
        <p class="text-base text-synthesis-500 mb-6">
          Memory Packs—verified and lineage-tracked—create that mechanism.
        </p>
        <p class="text-2xl md:text-3xl text-synthesis-800 dark:text-synthesis-200 font-medium">
          Your expertise becomes <span class="gradient-text">equity</span>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Navigation -->
  <section class="section-narrow border-t border-synthesis-100 dark:border-synthesis-900">
    <div class="container-wide">
      <div class="fade-section flex flex-wrap justify-center gap-6 text-base">
        <a href="/vision" class="text-synthesis-600 dark:text-synthesis-400 hover:text-accent-600 dark:hover:text-accent-400 transition-colors">
          ← The Vision
        </a>
        <a href="/how-it-works" class="text-synthesis-600 dark:text-synthesis-400 hover:text-accent-600 dark:hover:text-accent-400 transition-colors">
          How It Works
        </a>
        <a href="/node" class="text-synthesis-600 dark:text-synthesis-400 hover:text-accent-600 dark:hover:text-accent-400 transition-colors">
          Synthesis Node →
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>
